---
// FAQ accordion component with original styling
---

<div class="max-w-[800px] mx-auto">
  <!-- FAQ Item 1 -->
  <div class="border-b border-gray-200">
    <button 
      class="faq-button py-8 w-full text-left cursor-pointer flex justify-between items-center gap-8 group"
      aria-expanded="false"
      aria-controls="faq-1"
    >
      <span class="text-[20px] font-heading font-normal text-gray-900 leading-relaxed">
        Do you work on systems you didn't install?
      </span>
      <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-gray-100 flex items-center justify-center transition-colors group-hover:bg-gray-200">
        <div class="relative w-4 h-4">
          <!-- Horizontal line - always visible -->
          <div class="absolute top-1/2 left-0 w-full h-0.5 bg-gray-600 transform -translate-y-1/2"></div>
          <!-- Vertical line - rotates to horizontal when open -->
          <div class="faq-icon absolute top-0 left-1/2 w-0.5 h-full bg-gray-600 transform -translate-x-1/2 transition-transform duration-300"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </button>
    <div 
      id="faq-1" 
      class="faq-content overflow-hidden transition-all duration-500 ease-in-out max-h-0 opacity-0"
    >
      <div class="pb-8 text-gray-600 text-[14px] leading-[1.5] font-heading max-w-3xl">
        Yes! We repair all solar systems regardless of who installed them. Our technicians are trained on all major brands and can work with any system configuration. We'll ensure all repairs maintain your existing warranties.
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- FAQ Item 2 -->
