        Will repairs void panel/inverter warranties?
      </span>
      <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-gray-100 flex items-center justify-center transition-colors group-hover:bg-gray-200">
        <div class="relative w-4 h-4">
          <div class="absolute top-1/2 left-0 w-full h-0.5 bg-gray-600 transform -translate-y-1/2"></div>
          <div class="faq-icon absolute top-0 left-1/2 w-0.5 h-full bg-gray-600 transform -translate-x-1/2 transition-transform duration-300"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </button>
    <div 
