      class="faq-content overflow-hidden transition-all duration-500 ease-in-out max-h-0 opacity-0"
    >
      <div class="pb-8 text-gray-600 text-[14px] leading-[1.5] font-heading max-w-3xl">
        No, our repairs are designed to maintain all existing warranties. We use manufacturer-approved parts and follow all warranty guidelines. In fact, proper maintenance and repairs can help extend the life of your system.
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

